# Ignore Python source code and virtual environments in connectors
**/*.py
**/.venv/**
**/node_modules/**
**/__pycache__/**

# Any `*.disabled/` directory under model-paths is intentionally not part
# of the active set. dbt walks model-paths recursively and would otherwise
# parse `connectors/*/dbt.disabled/schema.yml` (sources for un-deployed
# connectors) and `silver/*.disabled/*.sql` (silver models that depend on
# those sources). Both produce false-positive errors.
**/*.disabled/**
